title: COP30 deal a compromise; Germany committed to fossil fuel exit: Envoy
description: The COP30 climate summit in Brazil ended with a compromise deal expanding financial aid but lacking a fossil fuel phase-out clause. German envoy Philipp Ackermann expressed satisfaction with the results but was critical of the US's absence.
